\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I see by the papers that secretary chase has resigned. Mr chase is a politician, and is ambitious; he has worked three years, with all his mighty intellect, for the presidency. In this he failed; he withdraws from the cabinet to further his own schemes. I may judge him harshly, but I can not forget fremont.}
